{"tid":1456044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［兩軍交戰守則］偽裝成對方人員，被捕後可即場槍決","createTime":"2019-08-12T09:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T09:59:42.000Z","uid":149630,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"625f7d11b078e87545bb01c3b260843cd3b78652","tid":1456044,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:40:02.000Z","msg":"兩軍交戰有守則，如果偽裝成對方人員，被捕後可即場槍決 ! <br />\n<br />\n1944年12月16日，盟軍登陸諾曼第後向德國逐步進逼，希特拉將所有兵力集中在比利時亞登地區，孤注一擲發動絕地反擊，展開突出部之役(Battle of Bulge)，並且派出由奧托.史科尼兹率領的一支受過特別訓練，並且能講流利美式英語的約160人特種部隊，穿上由戰俘身上獲得的美軍制服，裝備，武器及車輛，假扮成美軍，進行麒麟作戰(Operation Greif)。<br />\n<br />\n德軍特種部隊滲透到美軍後方，更改路標，制做混亂，誤導及趁機殺害毫無防範之小單位美軍。又佔據繆斯河上之橋樑，保障德軍進攻通道無阻，其後德軍反攻被盟軍瓦解，部隊遭到重創，損失約10萬兵員。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而被捕德軍特種部隊成員由於身穿美軍軍服，故不受日內瓦國際公約(Geneva Conventions)保護，兼且觸犯戰爭罪行，被美軍指揮官命令憲兵即場執行槍決。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sj5hbHh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsj5hbHh.jpg&h=22d7660b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sVQkTVD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsVQkTVD.jpg&h=a2941f2c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sukQwHi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsukQwHi.jpg&h=3ae0a35d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cOO27fE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcOO27fE.jpg&h=c9252d0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCredit by Royal Hong Kong Regiment - The Volunteers<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/712822242120609/posts/2436536723082477?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F712822242120609%2Fposts%2F2436536723082477%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=nSJvRvahoV7vX7tkwZxFzgKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=a2876cd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/712822242120609/posts/2436536723082477?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"2c8ce9e3dc602718fb7e718ef95c3e86ca8ce589","tid":1456044,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:48:35.000Z","msg":"做咩事都有後果"},{"pid":"dc558a3e5e64875ede126448d821753c2ad623b8","tid":1456044,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:51:34.000Z","msg":"我地一定要等到呢一幕！"},{"pid":"d38c522f074477255b5fccd31bc47bb719c8a70d","tid":1456044,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:55:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7375d90e09d422f629b45d41cd82baa88240d308","tid":1456044,"uid":298413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:59:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0872d5b71adf842fc62f17f1e4623001472808f0","tid":1456044,"uid":57554,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:59:42.000Z","msg":"國際禁用嘅中空子彈，黑警一樣照用多年<br />\n呢類條例都係戰爭先會管"}]}